title: Wholesale Price of Canned Tomatoes for New York, NY
notes:
Series Has Been Subdivided Into Three Variables: (1)-- Original Data, 1908-1938; (2)-- Original Data, 1937-1942; (3)-- Original Data, 1942-1951. Data Refers To The Price Of Standard Maryland #2 Cans, 24 Per Case Delivered At New York City. Source: 1937-1938: Unpublished Figures From Bls Files; 1939-1942: Bls Bulletins

This NBER data series m04042b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
